-find disk
-fix perms
-update vmdk
-lounch vm

--- in vm

-wait for disk
-open luks
-mount volume
-start vpn
-wait for remote-host
-ssh remote-host

--- on remote

-test reverse-connection
-unmount disks if mounted
-mount disks
-start restic
-unmount disks

--- in vm

-close vpn
-unmount volume
-close luks
-poweroff (or notify of possibility)
